    <title>清华托福慕课</title>
    <link href="/2021/08/12/%E6%89%98%E7%A6%8F%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87-b%E7%AB%99/"/>
    <url>/2021/08/12/%E6%89%98%E7%A6%8F%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87-b%E7%AB%99/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a class="btn" href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1LW411v7Z6?from=search&seid=13749202924051620964" title="bilibili链接">text</a></p><h1 id="阅读"><a href="#阅读" class="headerlink" title="阅读"></a>阅读</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2021-08-08%20%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%887.41.41.png"></p><h1 id="听力"><a href="#听力" class="headerlink" title="听力"></a>听力</h1><p>每天3小时，一个月</p><h2 id="阶段1-10天-TOP1-5"><a href="#阶段1-10天-TOP1-5" class="headerlink" title="阶段1       10天 TOP1-5"></a>阶段1       10天 TOP1-5</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.01.54%20AM.png"></p><ol><li>盲听一遍</li><li>按句听，完全还原每一句话所有单词（非常严格，吞音也要还原）（如果听不出来看原文）</li><li>把生词加入生词本</li><li>逐句听，模仿发音，包括所有发音特征 （5-10遍）</li><li>整体再听一遍，达标</li></ol><h2 id="阶段2-5天-TOP6-10"><a href="#阶段2-5天-TOP6-10" class="headerlink" title="阶段2        5天 TOP6-10"></a>阶段2        5天 TOP6-10</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.10.44%20AM.png"></p><ol><li>盲听两遍</li><li>拿着脚本听，对</li><li>生词</li><li>影子跟读（3-5遍）</li><li>整体再听一遍，达标</li></ol><h2 id="阶段3-5天-SSS-科学美国人"><a href="#阶段3-5天-SSS-科学美国人" class="headerlink" title="阶段3        5天 SSS 科学美国人"></a>阶段3        5天 SSS <a href="https://www.scientificamerican.com/podcasts/">科学美国人</a></h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.14.59%20AM.png"></p><p>SSS：帮你带入真正美国课堂的语速</p><ol><li>盲听2-3遍</li><li>对应脚本每个词</li><li>影子跟读</li><li>听一遍</li></ol><p><a href="open.163.com/ocw">泛听</a></p><h2 id="词性-gt-发音差异"><a href="#词性-gt-发音差异" class="headerlink" title="词性-&gt;发音差异"></a>词性-&gt;发音差异</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.23.07%20AM.png"></p><p>动词会把音放在中间</p><h2 id="常用简化发音"><a href="#常用简化发音" class="headerlink" title="常用简化发音"></a>常用简化发音</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.24.52%20AM.png"></p><h2 id="习惯性短语"><a href="#习惯性短语" class="headerlink" title="习惯性短语"></a>习惯性短语</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.26.50%20AM.png"></p><h2 id="Conversation"><a href="#Conversation" class="headerlink" title="Conversation"></a>Conversation</h2><h3 id="常见场景"><a href="#常见场景" class="headerlink" title="常见场景"></a>常见场景</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.28.59%20AM.png"></p><p>教授、员工特别负责，并且严格</p><p>女同学什么都做得好，</p><p>男同学一直听不懂，论文一直都写不好</p><p>实验永远都是操作有问题</p><p>加分、选课、毕业修分</p><h3 id="层次关系"><a href="#层次关系" class="headerlink" title="层次关系"></a>层次关系</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.33.45%20AM.png"></p><ul><li>Conversation</li><li>一般4-6个 layer </li><li>往往有一个主题</li><li>听清楚 case A， 是✅还是❌， 如何导出的case b</li></ul><h3 id="常见考点"><a href="#常见考点" class="headerlink" title="常见考点"></a>常见考点</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.36.13%20AM.png"></p><h2 id="Lecture"><a href="#Lecture" class="headerlink" title="Lecture"></a>Lecture</h2><h3 id="Lecture与阅读的关系"><a href="#Lecture与阅读的关系" class="headerlink" title="Lecture与阅读的关系"></a>Lecture与阅读的关系</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357015.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.43.31 AM"></p><h3 id="常见结构"><a href="#常见结构" class="headerlink" title="常见结构"></a>常见结构</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357587.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.45.59 AM"></p><h3 id="常见考点-1"><a href="#常见考点-1" class="headerlink" title="常见考点"></a>常见考点</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357380.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.47.38 AM"></p><h2 id="记笔记方法"><a href="#记笔记方法" class="headerlink" title="记笔记方法"></a>记笔记方法</h2><p>先左右分开，或者分三列</p><p>根据层次递进地听、记，最重要的是把层次听出来</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357766.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.49.06 AM"></p><p>并不是所有人都适合一开始就记笔记，如果一开始连一半都听不懂记笔记反而成为负担</p><p>大多数人是需要记笔记的</p><p>辅助记录，分析层次，答题时不需要回看笔记的</p><p>如果有人不加试，旁边的人会已经开始口语，影响自己注意力</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357519.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.52.43 AM"></p><h2 id="结语：量变到质变"><a href="#结语：量变到质变" class="headerlink" title="结语：量变到质变"></a>结语：量变到质变</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357709.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.55.35 AM"></p>]]></content>
    
    
